### 1. 注册用户
POST http://localhost:8081/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456",
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

### 2. 用户登录
POST http://localhost:8081/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 3. 重复注册（应失败）
POST http://localhost:8081/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456",
  "email": "test2@example.com"
}

### 4. 错误密码登录（应失败）
POST http://localhost:8081/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### 5. 不存在的用户（应失败）
POST http://localhost:8081/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "notexist",
  "password": "123456"
}
### 3. 获取用户信息（需要 Token）
GET http://localhost:8081/user/info
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxIiwidXNlcm5hbWUiOiJ0ZXN0dXNlciIsImlhdCI6MTc4NDA4MTQyNywiZXhwIjoxNzg0Njg2MjI3fQ.weAPJ9waKNfnLKjddNslsYy7909X1cIr_LSJEmNPRds
### 1. 管理员登录
POST http://localhost:8081/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 2. 管理员访问用户列表（应该成功）
GET http://localhost:8081/user/list
Authorization: Bearer <admin_token>

### 3. 普通用户登录
POST http://localhost:8081/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "normaluser",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 4. 普通用户访问用户列表（应该失败 403）
GET http://localhost:8081/user/list
Authorization: Bearer <normal_token>
